Package: RPostgreSQLHelper
Title: wrapper functions for the RPostgreSQL package to handle db
        connection failures, where connections are initialised via
        rapache config file.
Version: 1.0
Depends: RPostgreSQL
Date: 2013-03-20
Author: John Dickinson <jad@sinodun.com>
Maintainer: John Dickinson <jad@sinodun.com>
Description: Attempts to reconnect to the database if the
	connection has been lost and fails gracefully in
        the event that the connection to the database
        cannot be re-established.
License: GPL-3
Packaged: 2013-03-20 16:11:46 UTC; jad
